{
  "stem": "25114.6",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We almost stayed eight months in this base, like from the day like my daughter was born, like in November, end of November, till July '44, 10th of July.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How many months is this?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Seven, eight months?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It developed into-- into a town, a shtetl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Had everything.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You wouldn't believe what was-- we had tradesmen, we had builders, we had all sort of people from all different businesses that knew about everything.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So since they burnt out all the neighbor villages around the pushcha, in-- because they didn't want the partisan to have any resources.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So still there were a lot of things abandoned like ovens, and stoves, and doors, and windows, and frames of all kind of-- tools, things for utility sort of use.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the tradesmen, one of the first things they built was a bakery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you should've seen-- there was a special man who could build up such an oven with the help, of course, of-- had raw materials from the burned-out houses around all the villages.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we used to go and collect all those things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the first came a bakery-- first we finished off all the zemilyankas.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then came the bakery-- we needed bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then came the-- the-- of course, the warehouse where all the provisions were kept.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my husband was in charge.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then came the-- of course the doctors' offices.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then came a sausage factory.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had real tradesmen-- you should have seen the hams and the bacons and the salamis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And some of it was kosher, because we had the kosher butchers there [LAUGHS] in [NON-ENGLISH], and one was a-- And we had a mill, which we got-- took it from somewhere, from abandoned flour mill.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We had a tannery, made-- made leather.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
